{"tid":1616612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【和理非路線】你推蒙面法，我每日收工即刻返屋企，唔消費","createTime":"2019-10-03T13:15:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T05:45:21.000Z","uid":79382,"like":80,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"9da7aeef4fe9e7cddb9c5cb10af0106887e7b5b7","tid":1616612,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:15:14.000Z","msg":"原本已經俾狗畜搞到周街都唔安全，<br />\n仲要開咗緊急法先例，即係你突然做乜柒都得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我唯有每日收工，即刻搭車返屋企，<br />\n唔做額外消費，大幅減少出街食飯，<br />\n淨係幫襯雜貨、士多、超級市場，<br />\n放假盡量留返本區活動，<br />\n重返2003年嘅簡樸生活 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然未必即時有明顯效果，<br />\n但係咩方法都要試 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反正市民講嘢你唔撚聽㗎啦，<br />\n咪等班生意佬屌爆你老母囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd94628e3f128843011d5ff09b7548849fef0ac","tid":1616612,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:15:29.000Z","msg":"香港人俾政府恰到上心口！<br />\n「反蒙面法」有機會聽日立埋<br />\n如果你連三罷公投都唔表態<br />\n你 註定輸一世！<br />\n<br />\n公投截止日期：10月11日中午12點<br />\n<br />\nThe Government treat all HongKongers as nothing and they also want to pass the anti-mask law to tackle protesters.<br />\nIt is time for us to speak up! Let&rsquo;s give your opinion on performing general strike.<br />\n<br />\nDeadline: 11 Oct 2019 1200 HKT<br />\n<br />\n公投傳送門：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nWkSyo&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEtLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=71989226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo</a>"},{"pid":"ef0bdd64a5e846ada94873c337cd93400ac60403","tid":1616612,"uid":145225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:16:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">十月四前哨戰 全民口罩<br />\n十月五遊行 全民面具</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"5932e6d4632d929124ce0bdff3633e961e70eb6d","tid":1616612,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:17:41.000Z","msg":"有冇得諗？"},{"pid":"9e328d9328e70856088e51943324e3fe9d24ebc7","tid":1616612,"uid":34138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:18:32.000Z","msg":"一直都係咁"},{"pid":"158b7316aea660b91dab5234310446ab1dff368e","tid":1616612,"uid":79182,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:19:30.000Z","msg":"長期戰嚟<br />\n一出咩緊急法 蒙面法<br />\n我地就100% 唔消費<br />\n我唔信香港地可以無左100萬人消費都撐到"},{"pid":"260ad6784f729ee455e4ef16f2bd34c8fb115bdc","tid":1616612,"uid":245078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:19:58.000Z","msg":"6月到而家除左食，車錢已接近零消費"},{"pid":"599799cf606deb9c9032d5c8953e3a298f0d3fbd","tid":1616612,"uid":34334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:20:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a2727aef50c83bd4ce0abbab24a906f714732df0","tid":1616612,"uid":79382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"158b7316aea660b91dab5234310446ab1dff368e","tid":1616612,"uid":79182,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:19:30.000Z","msg":"長期戰嚟<br />\n一出咩緊急法 蒙面法<br />\n我地就100% 唔消費<br />\n我唔信香港地可以無左100萬人消費都撐到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:20:51.000Z","msg":"但真係要大規模文宣，<br />\n變成一種風氣，<br />\n香港人好懶的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85bd99666c7ff22acb9256d08b40b8ffa3c1ba4d","tid":1616612,"uid":26491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:21:23.000Z","msg":"罷工？好呀，求求你幫我塞左交通佢唔係我罷唔到，醫生紙唔易攞呀，年假冇哂啦，NO PAY LEAVE又唔太好<br />\n罷課？好呀，等我同學校商量一下，我照番學但唔上堂啦，唔番學校唔得架<br />\n罷買？原來係咁，明白明白，會同人講架啦，我本身都冇野要買架啦（好似係）<br />\n罷食？我窮呀，要食平野，其他又唔喺我附近，方便呀嘛，咁我都要食飯架唔通唔食呀？<br />\n<br />\n全民口罩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />